    "correctIndex": 1,
    "explanation": "Differentiating \\(3f(x)-2f(1/x)=x\\): \\(3f'(x)+\\dfrac{2}{x^2}f'(1/x)=1\\) …(i)\n\nAt \\(x=2\\): \\(3f'(2)+\\dfrac{1}{2}f'(1/2)=1\\) …(i)\n\nPutting \\(x=1/2\\) in original differentiated equation:\n\\(3f'(1/2)+8f'(2)=1\\) …(ii)\n\nSolving (i) and (ii): \\(f'(2)=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\).",
