    "correctIndex": 2,
    "explanation": "Using product rule:\n\n\\[\\frac{dy}{dx}=\\sin^{98}x\\cdot39\\cos^{38}x(-\\sin x)+\\cos^{39}x\\cdot98\\sin^{97}x(\\cos x)\\]\n\n\\[=98\\cos^{99}x\\cdot\\sin^{97}\\cdot\\cos x\\cdot x-39\\sin^{99}x\\cos^{38}x\\]\n\nSimplifying: \\(98\\cos^{99}x\\cdot\\sin^{38}x-39\\sin^{40}x\\cdot\\cos^{97}x\\)",
