    "correctIndex": 0,
    "explanation": "Simplifying: \\(f(x)=|\\sqrt{x-2}+\\sqrt{2}|+|\\sqrt{x-2}-\\sqrt{2}|\\).\n\nFor \\(x\\geq4\\): \\(f(x)=2\\sqrt{x-2}\\).\n\n\\(f'(x)=\\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{x-2}}\\)\n\n\\(10\\times f'(102)=10\\times\\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{100}}=10\\times\\dfrac{1}{10}=1\\)",
