    "correctIndex": 3,
    "explanation": "Taking log: \\(\\ln y=x+\\ln(\\ln x)-2\\ln x\\).\n\nDifferentiating: \\(\\dfrac{y'}{y}=1+\\dfrac{1}{x\\ln x}-\\dfrac{2}{x}\\).\n\n\\[y'=y\\cdot\\frac{x\\ln x+1-2\\ln x}{x\\ln x}=\\frac{e^x}{x^3}\\cdot\\frac{x\\ln x+1-2\\ln x}{\\ln x}=\\frac{e^x[1+(x-2)\\ln x]}{x^3}\\]",
